{"tid":2004293,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"死火牛定死板?","createTime":"2020-05-06T10:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T11:17:16.000Z","uid":40822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d11d729699d73736b29ea3cb137a992d107c83","tid":2004293,"uid":40822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有一日，突然之間開唔到機，所有風扇都無轉到 ! 跟著搞條ram，插來插去，之後開到機，但讀唔到harddisk同入唔到windows ! 攤左部機一陣，又係著唔返 !<br />\n<br />\n跟著換左新ram，又係咁 ! 試過用萬字夾試火牛風扇有冇轉到，結果係有轉到 ! <br />\n<br />\n如果24 pins 接落塊板，塊板一直長著LED ! 部機正常個陣，即使關左機，塊板有LED 閃下 !<br />\n<br />\n利申: asus底板"},{"pid":"a65f371cf9ae0c6c13fc19cc8cd50b3ec7c1cdac","tid":2004293,"uid":73907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"有冇蜂嗚器？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d782d9453c3069008fab7f502675d4d348b67fa","tid":2004293,"uid":40822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a65f371cf9ae0c6c13fc19cc8cd50b3ec7c1cdac","tid":2004293,"uid":73907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"有冇蜂嗚器？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"711fb86bc4a7f67052039110ae9c815f183c12bd","tid":2004293,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"有無試過甩開隻hdd試"},{"pid":"ecd842873a75f9d9b7cd8bfdec047b8ba7d07636","tid":2004293,"uid":40822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"711fb86bc4a7f67052039110ae9c815f183c12bd","tid":2004293,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"有無試過甩開隻hdd試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"有 ! 都係著唔機 !"},{"pid":"bb811d05835f9866bbc082960476f4e861150e5f","tid":2004293,"uid":283984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06